# Custom Font Placeholder

This directory will contain custom heading fonts once selected.

For now, the system will fall back to system fonts.

To add custom fonts:
1. Add .woff2 and .woff files to shared/fonts/
2. Name them custom-heading.woff2 and custom-heading.woff
3. Update design-tokens.css @font-face if needed

Font requirements:
- Impactful, confident style for headings
- Web-optimized formats (WOFF2 primary, WOFF fallback)
- Font weight range: 400-700 preferred

